@startuml sequence_add_story
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Add New Behavioral Story

actor Candidate
participant "Markdown Editor" as Editor
participant "story-bank.md" as StoryBank
participant "job-search Skill" as Skill

Candidate -> Editor : Open interview-prep/story-bank.md
Editor -> StoryBank : Read existing content
StoryBank --> Editor : Return current stories

Candidate -> Editor : Append new STAR+Reflection block\n(with skills, keywords, context tags)
Editor -> StoryBank : Write appended file\n(existing entries unchanged)
StoryBank --> Editor : Save confirmed

Candidate -> Skill : Run job-search (next cycle)
Skill -> StoryBank : Read story bank
StoryBank --> Skill : Return all stories including new entry
Skill -> Skill : Validate tags present on all stories
Skill --> Candidate : Confirm story registered;\nwarn if any story missing required tags

@enduml
